tists/tom-meighan">Tom Meighan</a>的情况下在维多利亚公园演出。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-confirm-departure-of-singer-tom-meighan-after-struggle-with-personal-issues-2702190">于 2020 年离开乐队</a>，仅仅一天后就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-kasabian-singer-tom-meighan-pleads-guilty-to-assaulting-former-fiancee-2703002">因虐待搭档 Vikki Ager 被定罪，</a>并在认罪后在莱斯特地方法院被判处<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-kasabian-frontman-tom-meighan-issues-statement-following-assault-charge-partner-vikki-rehab-apology-2703977">200 小时无薪工作</a>。</p><p>梅根后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-tom-meighan-assault-adhd-mental-health-rehab-solo-music-cancel-culture-3057235">解释说，他“多年来一直与酒瘾作斗争</a>”，并将这些事件视为“警钟”。他和阿格尔后来结婚了， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-tom-meighan-assault-adhd-mental-health-rehab-solo-music-cancel-culture-3057235">梅根被诊断出患有多动症，并表示他对自己的虐待行为“深感羞愧”</a> 。</p><p>他于 2021 年底<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-meighan-shares-debut-solo-single-would-you-mind-as-a-free-download-3082543">开始了个人职业生涯</a>，并在许多头条节目和节日演出中演出。他的首张个人专辑《The Reckoning》于五月发行。今年夏天，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-announce-2023-outdoor-essex-show-dates-buy-tickets-3358822">在埃塞克斯举行的 Heritage Live 演出</a>中为诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 提供了支持，然后又加入了他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-announces-tom-meighan-as-2023-uk-arena-tour-support-act-3479475">最近的竞技场巡演，</a>但谢菲尔德音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/be-reyt-festival-sheffield-tom-meighan-headline-kasabian-response-3430234">Be Reyt 因因梅根的虐待罪而预订了梅根而受到广泛批评</a>。</p><p> Meighan 离开后，乐队成员 Serge Pizzorno 接任主唱，并于 2022 年 8 月发行了由他主唱的第一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kasabian-the-alchemists-euphoria-review-3285302">The Alchemist&#39;s Euphoria</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-announce-new-album-happenings-along-with-huge-summer-solstice-ii-leicester-show-with-kaiser-chiefs-3553082">Kasabian 宣布新专辑《Happenings》以及与 Kaiser Chiefs 一起在莱斯特举办的大型演出《夏至 II》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
